  <text>
     <body>
     <div type="poem">
   <pb n="350" facs="185"/>
   <lg>
      <l>Some only learne for knowledge sake,</l>
      <l>but that is curiositie:</l>
      <l>And some for praise, great paines do take,</l>
      <l>but that is foolish vanitie.</l>
      <l>Some learne for gaine, but lightly those,</l>
      <l>do leaue the text, and vse the gloze.</l>
      <l>But learning ioynd, with vertues lore,</l>
      <l>doth leade to Christianitie:</l>
      <l>The glory of God, and people taught,</l>
      <l>the way is to eternitie.</l>
   </lg>
</div>
